name: UFAlert(Unofficial)
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: This Unofficial UF Alert Alexa Skill takes the RSS Feed from the UF Alert page and allows you to get any status updates just by including it in your flash briefing!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
